  "name": "Agents only - Turning on Feature flags",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"agents-only-turning-on-feature-flags\">Agents only - Turning on Feature flags</h1>\n<p>Feature flags are the ability to turn on/off features within a customer database. Previously this was typically managed within MGMT, however this is now being moved directly within the database itself (this aids with future development purposes).</p>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>Currently the features are not specifically designed to be switched <em>off</em> i.e. \"test this feature out, then we'll switch it off again\". Features should only be switched on when appropriate for licensing or internal testing purposes.</p>\n</div>\n<h2 data-id=\"turning-on-a-feature-flag\">Turning on a feature flag</h2>\n<p>To turn on a feature flag you will need to do the following:</p>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>You will need the Retail Express \"god mode\" login - credentials can be obtained from your manager</p>\n</div>\n<ol><li>Log into Retail Express</li><li>Navigate to <strong>Settings &gt; Global Settings</strong></li><li>Scroll down to <strong>7. Feature Settings</strong></li><li>Tick the required feature</li><li>Click <strong>Save Changes</strong></li></ol><p><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"137\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nMHKrEAO.png\" width=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 137px; width: 500px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nMHKrEAO.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nMHKrEAO.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nMHKrEAO.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nMHKrEAO.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nMHKrEAO.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nMHKrEAO.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nMHKrEAO.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<h2 data-id=\"customer-view\">Customer view</h2>\n<p>When the customer logs in and navigates to the Global Settings they will see section 7 as the web store:</p>\n<p><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"313\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nMHLaEAO.png\" width=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 313px; width: 500px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nMHLaEAO.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nMHLaEAO.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nMHLaEAO.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nMHLaEAO.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nMHLaEAO.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nMHLaEAO.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nMHLaEAO.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>",
